  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网边缘节点的批处理工作流设计一个状态图。核心场景是：EdgeNode收到批次后启动任务，最终由ActuatorController执行，或者失败时流向TelemetryStream上报。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "Batch",
        "Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。让我确认一下层级：Batch.Received.Event作为起点触发Batch.Started.State，然后拆分为单个Job？还是批次和任务是并行的两条线？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Batch.Received.Event",
        "Batch.Started.State",
        "Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是层级关系。Batch.Started.State之后产生Job.Received.Event，进入Job.Received.State。每个Job走完自己的生命周期后，通过Batch.Job.Done.Event汇总到Batch.Finished.State，最终交给ActuatorController。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Batch.Started.State",
        "Job.Received.Event",
        "Job.Received.State",
        "Batch.Job.Done.Event",
        "Batch.Finished.State",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，主流程已绘制：EdgeNode→Batch.Received.Event→Batch.Started.State→Job.Received.Event→Job.Received.State→Job.Completed.Event→Job.Completed.State→Batch.Job.Done.Event→Batch.Finished.State→ActuatorController。异常分支需要怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "Batch.Received.Event",
        "Batch.Started.State",
        "Job.Received.Event",
        "Job.Received.State",
        "Job.Completed.Event",
        "Job.Completed.State",
        "Batch.Job.Done.Event",
        "Batch.Finished.State",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Job层面需要失败分支：Job.Received.State可以走到Job.Failed.Event，进入Job.Failed.State，然后汇总到Batch.Job.Done.Failed.Event。另外MQTT Broker也要能触发批次接收失败的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Job.Received.State",
        "Job.Failed.Event",
        "Job.Failed.State",
        "Batch.Job.Done.Failed.Event",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "Batch.Received.Failed.Event"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "两个失败终点都流向TelemetryStream吗？还是只有Batch层面的失败才上报？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Job.Failed.State",
        "Batch.Failed.State",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Batch.Job.Done.Failed.Event进入Batch.Failed.State后流向TelemetryStream；MQTT Broker触发的Batch.Received.Failed.Event也直接进入Batch.Failed.State。Job.Failed.State本身不直接连TelemetryStream，必须先汇总到批次层面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Batch.Job.Done.Failed.Event",
        "Batch.Failed.State",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "Batch.Received.Failed.Event",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "Job.Failed.State"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。现在图中有两条失败汇聚路径：Job失败通过Batch.Job.Done.Failed.Event汇总，以及MQTT Broker直接触发的接收失败，都进入Batch.Failed.State最终上报到TelemetryStream。主成功流向ActuatorController，结构清晰了。",
